<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Entering students who have satisfactorily completed College Board Advanced Placement courses and who present scores of 3 or higher on Advanced Placement Examinations will automatically receive appropriate course credit toward a degree. A student presenting such grades for the equivalent of 27 semester hours of courses will be awarded immediate sophomore standing at Campbellsville University.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.campbellsville.edu/cat-admissions#advance" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
